{"tid":664357,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"已婚男騙貞操、斬她姻緣！　小三獲償10萬","createTime":"2018-05-14T04:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T04:36:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5e8b825b5a74b6ceac5af4824d6f743182b0ac48","tid":664357,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:31:50.000Z","msg":"已婚江男對吳女死纏爛打追求，奪走初夜後，要她「不要計較名分」，吳女憤而提告求償。法官認定吳女人格尊嚴受侵害，判決江男需賠償10萬元。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，吳女2014年間與江男相識，江男展開追求，她考量江男已婚，且自己也有論及婚嫁對象而拒絕。江以「與配偶感情不佳，即將離婚」說服她交往，甚至自殘威脅、到她住處按門鈴騷擾。她不得已答應交往，並與男友分手。<br />\n<br />\n不料江根本沒處理離婚事宜，騙取她貞操後，說服她不要要求名分，吳女求償70萬元。法官認為，江男已婚，卻死纏爛打吳女，造成吳女心理上壓迫，已侵害她人格尊嚴，判賠10萬元。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180514/640_3056ce892bec9ed3341118a9256c5532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180514%2F640_3056ce892bec9ed3341118a9256c5532.jpg&h=bc26e63b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180514/1353273/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180514%2F1353273%2F&d=BzsFvvO4moS6CNL1%2FM7kiIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=bc6a1080\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180514%2F1353273%2F&h=16774daf\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180514/1353273/</a>"},{"pid":"f4cc20b40c305929ca05dd9fd08d99c0ed7937bf","tid":664357,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:36:24.000Z","msg":"樓主係台灣人？咁關心呢啲台灣無聊新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}